{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place quinoa and 250 g water in mixing bowl then cook <b>15 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>. Transfer into a large serving bowl and set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place 3 sprigs parsley and lemon zest in mixing bowl then grate <b>10 sec\/speed 9<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then grate again <b>10 sec\/speed 9<b> until a fine consistency is achieved. Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Place garlic and chilli in mixing bowl then chop <b>3 sec\/speed 7<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add 30 g olive oil and sauté <b>2 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Transfer into bowl with lemon and parsley and set aside.","Without rinsing mixing bowl, place remaining 1000 g water in mixing bowl. Place Varoma into position, insert Varoma tray then weigh salmon fillets onto Varoma tray.","Cover salmon fillets with reserved lemon and garlic mixture, then secure Varoma lid and cook <b>14-18 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>, or until salmon is cooked to your liking. Set Varoma aside and allow salmon to cool. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Once salmon has cooled, use a fork to break into pieces, then transfer into large serving bowl with the quinoa and set aside.","Place red pepper, onion, cucumber,  basil, mustard, vinegar, remaining 3 sprigs parsley, salt, pepper 100 g feta and remaining 30 g olive oil in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 4<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add tomatoes, avocado and half of the chives then combine <b>10 sec\/\/speed 2<b>.","Place kale into large serving bowl with the quinoa and salmon pieces, then add chopped salad mixture and gently toss to combine. Sprinkle with pumpkin seeds, dried cranberries, remaining 1 tbsp chives and remaining 50 g feta. Serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["100 g tri-colour quinoa","1250 g water","6 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only","½ lemon, zest only, no white pith","1 garlic clove","½ long red chilli","60 g olive oil","600 g fresh boneless, skinless salmon fillet","1 red pepper, deseeded and cut into eighths","½ red onion, cut into halves","1 cucumber, cut into pieces","3 sprigs fresh basil, leaves only","1 tsp Dijon mustard","1 tbsp apple cider vinegar","½ tsp sea salt","2 pinches ground black pepper","150 g feta cheese","300 g vine-ripened tomatoes, cut into pieces (2 cm)","1 avocado, flesh only, thinly sliced","2 tbsp fresh chives, thinly sliced","100 g kale, thinly sliced","1 tbsp pumpkin seeds","2 tbsp dried cranberries"]}],"id":"r123529","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-UCyKrF1p2po\/XZMvdVS-e-I\/AAAAAAAAaSE\/1UhSmj4rsQsrgRiDlNfPNaMMTxm8L6l6QCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_gQ1MWrbeNxbQlh4g.png","title":"Superfood Salmon Salad","publishedAt":"2017-03-20T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"37 g","fat":"39 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"17 g","calories":"2435 kJ \/ 579 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large serving bowl","basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 5m","6 portions"]}